title: EQUIPMENT + RESOURCES REQUIRED - SERGE LAMP
---



<p> -	EQUIPMENT:</p>
<p>-	LASER CUTTER</p>
<p>-	CIRCUIT ROUTER (ROLAND)</p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p>-	ELECTRONICS:</p>
<p>SOLDERING IRON</p>
<p>ATTINY45</p>
<p>5V 100mA REGULATOR</p>
<p>4 x RESISTER (0)</p>
<p>10k RESISTER </p>
<p>6mm DC POWER JACK</p>
<p>2x2 HEADER PINS</p>
<p>2x3 HEADER PINS</p>
<p>ULTRASONIC MOTION SENSOR</p>
<p>12V LED STRIP (12 LEDS)</p>
<p>N-CHANNEL MOSFET</p>
<p>WIRE</p>
<p>12V POWER SUPPLY WITH 6mm ADAPTER PLUG</p>
<p>AVR PROGRAMMER</p>
<p>CIRCUIT BOARD</p>
<p></p>
<p>-	LAMP FORM:</p>
<p>-	6mm POPLAR PLY (approx. 1100x600, design dependent)</p>
<p>-	ARADITE GLUE</p>
<p>-	ALUMINUM ROD 10mm x 580mm</p>
<p>
<p>-	PROGRAMMES:</p>
<p>-	ARDUINO</p>
<p>-	EAGLE</p>
<p>-	ADOBE ILLUSTRATOR</p>
